FT  23 FEB 94 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Johannesburg saw a quiet day with most stocks little changed on the session.
Both the gold and industrial indices shed 7, to 1,855 and 5,697
respectively. The overall index slipped 9 to 4,822. De Beers finished R1
down at R104.50.
